2. Bundled/generated frame data and character/animation references
------------------------------------------------------------------

The files under `frames/` are generated Braille terminal-art frame data derived from
credited Aris animation references. They are included so the `arisusay` binary can run
without downloading or decoding external media at runtime.

To the extent ArisuSay contributors hold rights in the generated Braille frame data,
they permit use, copying, modification, and redistribution of that generated frame data
as part of this project, its source distribution, and built `arisusay` binaries.

This permission does not grant any trademark, character, game, illustration,
animation, music, video, or other rights owned by Nexon, Blue Archive rights holders,
청세치 / 세치혀, or any other original creator or rights holder. No ownership of Tendou
Aris, Blue Archive, or the original animation sources is claimed.

If a rights holder asks for removal or replacement of the referenced/generated art
assets, the project should comply by removing or replacing the affected frame data.
